'''AnchorFree'''是一家互聯網隱私和安全公司，為企業和消費者提供先進的技術，以實現安全和私人的網路瀏覽。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/anchorfree-vpn-business-booming-net-neutrality-repeal-hacks-2018-2|title=This software startup had its best year ever and the CEO says the end of net neutrality is a big reason why|last=Sandler|first=Rachel|website=Business Insider|access-date=2019-04-16|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616131949/https://www.businessinsider.com/anchorfree-vpn-business-booming-net-neutrality-repeal-hacks-2018-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2018/09/05/anchorfree-maker-of-hotspot-shield-raises-295-million-in-new-funding/|title=AnchorFree, maker of Hotspot Shield, raises $295 million in new funding|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US|access-date=2019-04-16}}</ref>該公司的旗艦產品是 [[Hotspot_Shield|Hotspot Shield]]，這是一種[[VPN|VPN]]服務，並且該應用程式在App Store被評選為生產力最高的應用程式。<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/05/technology/anchorfree-vpn-hotspot-shield.html|title=AnchorFree, Maker of a Top Online Privacy App, Raises $295 Million|last=Griffith|first=Erin|date=2018-09-05|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-04-16|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033343/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/05/technology/anchorfree-vpn-hotspot-shield.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>大衛·哥羅德斯基（{{link-en|David Gorodyansky|David Gorodyansky}}）與他的朋友尤金·馬洛伯茨基（Eugene Malobrodsky）於2005年共同創立了該公司。<ref name="1CB">{{cite web|url=http://www.crunchbase.com/company/anchorfree|title=AnchorFree|work=CrunchBase|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2014-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410161719/http://www.crunchbase.com/company/anchorfree|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="2TF">{{cite web|last=Konrad|first=Alex|title=AnchorFree: A road warrior's friend, a censor's foe|url=http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2012/03/30/anchorfree-vpn-gorodyansky|work=CNN Money|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2013-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516153116/http://tech.fortune.cnn.com/2012/03/30/anchorfree-vpn-gorodyansky/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="3TC">{{cite web|last=Empson|first=Rip|title=With its Hotspot Shield hitting 60M Downloads, AnchorFree Lands a Whopping $52M from Goldman Sachs|url=https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/21/anchorfree-goldman-series-c|work=TechCrunch|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212010943/https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/21/anchorfree-goldman-series-c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>AnchorFree的總部位於加利福尼亞州紅木城，且在烏克蘭和俄羅斯設有辦事處。<ref name=":1" /> 2018年的最新一輪融資為該公司帶來了2.95億美元，使其總資金達到3.58億美元。<ref name="#1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/05/technology/anchorfree-vpn-hotspot-shield.html|title=AnchorFree, Maker of a Top Online Privacy App, Raises $295 Million|last=Griffith|first=Erin|date=2018-09-05|work=The New York Times|access-date=2019-04-26|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033343/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/09/05/technology/anchorfree-vpn-hotspot-shield.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
