==平臺和用戶==
該公司使用“ [[免費增值|免費增值]] ”的商業模式。以其旗艦產品[[Hotspot_Shield|Hotspot Shield]]爲例，其免費版提供具有一般功能的基本版軟體和具有某些增強功能的付費版本軟體<ref name="#2">{{Cite web|url=http://social.techcrunch.com/2012/05/21/anchorfree-goldman-series-c/|title=With Its Hotspot Shield Hitting 60M Downloads, AnchorFree Lands A Whopping $52M From Goldman Sachs|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US|access-date=2019-04-16}}</ref> ，例如虛擬服務器位置，更高的速度，無限的帶寬和AnchorFree的 ydra技術的24/7實時支援。<ref name="6TC">{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/31/anchorfree-brings-their-hotspot-shield-mobile-security-app-to-android|title=AnchorFree brings their Hotspot Shield mobile security app to Android|last=Velazco|first=Chris|work=TechCrunch|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127205102/https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/31/anchorfree-brings-their-hotspot-shield-mobile-security-app-to-android/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

AnchorFree的應用程序可用使用于[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]，[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]，[[Android|Android]]和[[iOS|iOS]] 操作系統的台式機和移動設備 。<ref name="6TC" /><ref name="7TNW">{{cite web|last=Messeih|first=Nancy|title=Hotspot Shield: A quiet hero for Internet privacy and security around the world|url=https://thenextweb.com/insider/2011/10/23/hotspot-shield-a-quiet-hero-for-Internet-privacy-and-security-around-the-world|work=TNW|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029022222/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2011/10/23/hotspot-shield-a-quiet-hero-for-internet-privacy-and-security-around-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該軟件下載量達6.5億次<ref name=":4" />，並在200多個國家/地區使用。<ref name="1CB" />此外，全球60％的知名安全公司和許多全球電信公司都使用AnchorFree的專有技術。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.techradar.com/news/anchorfree-why-our-vpn-can-ensure-fair-internet-for-all|title=AnchorFree: Why our VPN can ensure fair internet for all|last=VPN|first=TechRadar Pro 2018-10-10T15:01:30Z|website=TechRadar|language=en|access-date=2019-04-16|archive-date=2019-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416112925/https://www.techradar.com/news/anchorfree-why-our-vpn-can-ensure-fair-internet-for-all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3" />

在互聯網受到審查的國家/地區，[[Hotspot_Shield|Hotspot Shield]]是一款重要的應用程序。該應用程序允許用戶私密安全地訪問受限制的網站。<ref name=F /><ref name=8TNW>{{cite web|last=Messieh|first=Nancy|title=Hotspot Shield: A quiet hero for Internet privacy and security around the world|url=https://thenextweb.com/insider/2011/10/23/hotspot-shield-a-quiet-hero-for-Internet-privacy-and-security-around-the-world|work=TNW|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029022222/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2011/10/23/hotspot-shield-a-quiet-hero-for-internet-privacy-and-security-around-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該公司報告稱，在2010年[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]期間，其[[埃及|埃及]]用戶群從100,000個增加到100萬。<ref name="F">{{cite web|last=Colao|first=J.J.|title=How To Thwart Hackers And Dictators With One Free Download|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jjcolao/2012/08/29/how-to-thwart-hackers-and-dictators-with-one-free-download|publisher=Forbes|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2019-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190416185633/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jjcolao/2012/08/29/how-to-thwart-hackers-and-dictators-with-one-free-download/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="5Inc">{{cite web|last=Markowitz|first=Eric|title=David Gorodyansky and Eugene Malobrodsky, Founders of AnchorFree|url=http://www.inc.com/30under30/2011/profile-david-gorodyansky-eugene-malobrodsky-founders-anchorfree.html|work=Inc|accessdate=2013-04-08|archive-date=2019-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190623202811/https://www.inc.com/30under30/2011/profile-david-gorodyansky-eugene-malobrodsky-founders-anchorfree.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此期間，該程序用於訪問[[Twitter|Twitter]]等社交媒體網站組織抗議活動。<ref name="F" /><ref name="5Inc" />它在[[阿拉伯之春|阿拉伯之春]]之前也用於[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]和[[利比亞|利比亞]]。<ref name=8TNW />

2012年，在[[Hotspot_Shield|Hotspot Shield]]的下載量達到6000萬之後，該公司宣布已從[[高盛|高盛]]（Goldman Sachs）籌集了5200萬美元的融資。<ref name=techcrunch>{{cite web|url=https://www.techcrunch.com/2012/05/21/anchorfree-goldman-series-c/|title=With Its Hotspot Shield Hitting 60M Downloads, AnchorFree Lands A Whopping $52M From Goldman Sachs|last=Empson|first=Rip|date=2012-05-21|publisher=Tech Crunch|accessdate=2014-05-07|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212010943/https://techcrunch.com/2012/05/21/anchorfree-goldman-series-c/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==評論與所獲獎項==
2019年1月，{{link-en|TechRadar|TechRadar}}授予AnchorFree的[[Hotspot_Shield|Hotspot Shield]] 4星（滿分5星）評分，<ref name="#2"/><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.techradar.com/reviews/hotspot-shield-vpn|title=Hotspot Shield VPN review|last=Williams 2019-04-08T09:42:40ZUtilities|first=Mike|website=TechRadar|language=en|access-date=2019-04-16|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120081651/https://www.techradar.com/reviews/hotspot-shield-vpn|dead-url=no}}</ref>稱其為“''重視速度的用戶的高級VPN''”。評論家邁克·威廉姆斯（Mike Williams）總結說：''“如果網路瀏覽速度是您的重中之重，則其高速的性能可以完全達到這一點。”''<ref name=":2" />

2019年，《[[Fast_Company|Fast Company]]》將AnchorFree評選為全球第13名最具創新性的公司和第1名最具創新性的安全公司。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fastcompany.com/most-innovative-companies/2019|title=The World’s 50 Most Innovative Companies of 2019|website=Fast Company|language=en-US|access-date=2019-04-29|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115051609/https://www.fastcompany.com/most-innovative-companies/2019|dead-url=no}}</ref>

